 {"id":"coding_agent_session_search-23ltu","title":"Implement inline JavaScript for interactivity","description":"# Task: Inline JavaScript for Interactivity

## Context
The exported HTML needs interactive features that work offline. All critical JS must
be embedded, with CDN libraries (Prism.js) providing enhanced features when available.

## Core Features (Offline-Required)

### 1. Theme Toggle
```javascript
function toggleTheme() {
    const html = document.documentElement;
    const current = html.getAttribute('data-theme');
    const next = current === 'dark' ? 'light' : 'dark';
    html.setAttribute('data-theme', next);
    localStorage.setItem('cass-theme', next);
}

// Load saved preference
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const saved = localStorage.getItem('cass-theme');
    if (saved) document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', saved);
});
```

### 2. Search Within Conversation
```javascript
function searchConversation(query) {
    const messages = document.querySelectorAll('.message-content');
    let found = 0;

    messages.forEach(el => {
        el.innerHTML = el.textContent; // Reset highlights
        if (query && el.textContent.toLowerCase().includes(query.toLowerCase())) {
            const regex = new RegExp(`(${escapeRegex(query)})`, 'gi');
            el.innerHTML = el.textContent.replace(regex, '<mark>$1</mark>');
            found++;
        }
    });

    updateSearchStatus(found, query);
}
```

### 3. Collapsible Sections
```javascript
document.querySelectorAll('details.tool-call').forEach(el => {
    el.addEventListener('toggle', () => {
        // Animate height
        const content = el.querySelector('.tool-content');
        if (el.open) {
            content.style.maxHeight = content.scrollHeight + 'px';
        }
    });
});
```

### 4. Copy to Clipboard
```javascript
async function copyToClipboard(elementId) {
    const el = document.getElementById(elementId);
    try {
        await navigator.clipboard.writeText(el.textContent);
        showToast('Copied to clipboard');
    } catch (e) {
        // Fallback for older browsers
        const range = document.createRange();
        range.selectNode(el);
        window.getSelection().addRange(range);
        document.execCommand('copy');
        showToast('Copied to clipboard');
    }
}
```

### 5. Toast Notifications
```javascript
function showToast(message, type = 'info') {
    const toast = document.createElement('div');
    toast.className = `toast toast-${type}`;
    toast.textContent = message;
    document.body.appendChild(toast);

    // Animate in
    requestAnimationFrame(() => toast.classList.add('show'));

    // Auto dismiss
    setTimeout(() => {
        toast.classList.remove('show');
        setTimeout(() => toast.remove(), 300);
    }, 3000);
}
```

### 6. Print Handler
```javascript
function printConversation() {
    // Expand all collapsed sections before print
    document.querySelectorAll('details').forEach(d => d.open = true);
    window.print();
}
```

### 7. Keyboard Shortcuts
```javascript
document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
    // Ctrl/Cmd + F: Focus search
    if ((e.ctrlKey || e.metaKey) && e.key === 'f') {
        e.preventDefault();
        document.getElementById('search-input').focus();
    }
    // Ctrl/Cmd + P: Print
    if ((e.ctrlKey || e.metaKey) && e.key === 'p') {
        e.preventDefault();
        printConversation();
    }
    // Escape: Clear search
    if (e.key === 'Escape') {
        document.getElementById('search-input').value = '';
        searchConversation('');
    }
});
```

## CDN-Enhanced Features

### 8. Syntax Highlighting (Prism.js)
```javascript
// Only runs if Prism is loaded from CDN
if (typeof Prism !== 'undefined') {
    Prism.highlightAll();

    // Add copy buttons to code blocks
    document.querySelectorAll('pre code').forEach((block, i) => {
        const btn = document.createElement('button');
        btn.className = 'copy-code-btn';
        btn.onclick = () => copyToClipboard(`code-${i}`);
        block.id = `code-${i}`;
        block.parentNode.appendChild(btn);
    });
}
```

## Size Budget
Target: < 8KB minified JS (inline)
- Core interactivity: ~4KB
- Search: ~1.5KB
- Utilities: ~1KB
- Animations: ~1.5KB

## No-JS Fallback
Document must remain readable without JS:
- Content visible
- Navigation links work
- Print still functional (browser native)
- Only interactivity disabled

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Theme toggle persists across page loads
- [ ] Search highlights matches correctly
- [ ] Copy works in all major browsers
- [ ] Keyboard shortcuts documented and working
- [ ] No-JS fallback provides readable content
